  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age &gt; 18 yrs

          -  scheduled surgery

          -  General anesthesia

          -  ASA I to III

          -  Able to use a VAS

          -  No psychological disorders, able to speak french

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age &lt; 18 yrs

          -  Locoregional anesthesia or analgesia

          -  Allergia to morphine or ketamine

          -  Morphine or ketamine contraindication

          -  Pregnancy or breast-feeding
      </textblock>
